\item \textbf{Chapter 8 — Navier–Stokes.} P04 + finite-kernel (V1) + DCGT.
\item \textbf{Chapter 9 — MHD and Yang–Mills.} Chapter 8's content + T17 (Chapter 6) + DCGT non-Abelian extension.
\item \textbf{Chapter 10 — Soft-Matter Mobility.} P04 + V5 finite-width kernel + DCGT.
