\item \textbf{Chapter 12 — Curvature Emergence.} Chapter 11 + the substrate cumulative-strain four-index object as load-bearing curvature degree of freedom.
\item \textbf{Chapter 13 — Black-Hole Architecture.} P01 + P04 + P11 + finite-kernel + DCGT + the single substrate condition $|\nabla\rho|\,\ell_P^2/\rho_\mathrm{local} \gtrsim \log(R_\mathrm{cg}/\ell_P)$.
\item \textbf{Chapters 14–15.} Cross-platform unifications and empirical synthesis. Inherit dependencies from all preceding chapters.
\end{itemize}

This dependency graph is the program's audit trail. Any claim made in any chapter is traceable to a subset of the thirteen primitives plus mathematical structure.

