\item \textbf{T17's coverage} of Abelian and non-Abelian compact-simple-group structures.
\item \textbf{The interface-property origin} of gauge invariance.
\item \textbf{Substrate-level UV-finiteness} from P01 + P13 + P04.
\item \textbf{The reframing of renormalization} as a continuum-approximation tool rather than a substrate-level requirement.
\item \textbf{ED-I-13's substrate channel-geometry vocabulary} for quantum information (multiplicity, channels, identity alignment, global participation, rewrite-on-measurement).
\item \textbf{The substrate-level reinterpretation of the five landmark QI results} as channel-geometry manipulations.
\item \textbf{The structural unification} of QI under substrate channel geometry (replacing the standard treatment as five distinct Hilbert-space tricks).
\end{itemize}

\subsection{6.8.2 What is value-INHERITED}

