\item \textbf{Specific gauge couplings} (the fine structure constant $\alpha$, the strong coupling $\alpha_s$, the weak couplings, the Higgs vacuum expectation value). Empirical input.
\item \textbf{Specific particle masses} in the Standard Model. Empirical input.
