\item \textbf{Empirical confirmation of $\Gamma_\mathrm{cross}$-collapse cross-scale identity} in additional sectors beyond BH horizons and QC condition (ii). Cosmic-horizon and Rindler-horizon empirical content provides additional anchors when available.
\end{itemize}

