\item \textbf{O-QC-5: surface-code logical-qubit recursive-overlay derivation.} Specific scaling of $\tau_\mathrm{QC}^\mathrm{logical}$ with code distance and threshold from the substrate-level error-correction-as-meta-architecture analysis.
