\item \textbf{Condensed-matter and photonics sector (Chapter 8 plus extensions):} approximately 10 empirical claims (mesoscopic transport, SC phase-stiffness, Casimir-gradient, microresonator linewidth, photonic-crystal limit, comb formation, soliton step, Krieger-Dougherty, DST, plus others).
